<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>If a table name is passed to Zend\Db\Sql\Select object when creating it, the tableReadOnly property is set to true.</p>

<p>If one wants to check later on in the code if that property is set to true, it can't be done, as tableReadOnly is protected and Sql\Select has no isTableReadOnly() or getTableReadOnly() methods.</p>

